{"tid":1298229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完報道講抗爭者當中不乏少數族裔有感而發","createTime":"2019-07-08T22:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T01:28:39.000Z","uid":269774,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69d738e3606b2ece3520b7c63088dae25b2546b2","tid":1298229,"uid":269774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:56:29.000Z","msg":"利申：新牌仔第一個post<br />\n睇完呢篇文有感而發<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/06/home-i-want-hong-kongs-ethnic-minority-protesters-identity-belonging/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F07%2F06%2Fhome-i-want-hong-kongs-ethnic-minority-protesters-identity-belonging%2F&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=abdc3ebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/06/home-i-want-hong-kongs-ethnic-minority-protesters-identity-belonging/</a><br />\n香港有唔少非中國裔嘅香港人 佢哋有好多都好愛香港 好肯為香港付出 原因只有一個 就係香港係佢哋屋企<br />\n以下兩段我覺得值得反思<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;A lot of [minorities] feel that it is quite pointless. I was speaking to a lot of elder minorities and [they say] &lsquo;What&rsquo;s the point, China is going to do what they want.&rsquo;  But I&rsquo;m like, no, we can stop them.&rdquo;<br />\n我一直對2047好絕望 認為香港走唔甩一定冇自由冇普選 一定俾中共玩殘玩爛<br />\n但見到近排國際間對香港嘅關心程度我開始有啲動搖 雖然仲未一個國家有任何實質行動去救香港 起碼有返啲希望 知道我哋並不孤單 只要唔係甘心做奴隸嘅人 民主自由仍然係普世價值<br />\n喺爭取國際支持上 文宣組眾籌全球登報紙廣告應記一功 佔領立法會同持續示威遊行亦功不可沒 警察發癲使用過份武力亦令國際間更多人企喺我哋呢邊<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We&rsquo;re not ethnically Chinese, so immediately people think we&rsquo;re not from here. But this is home. My family has been here for three generations. If I have kids this will be home, so if we don&rsquo;t stand up now, who&rsquo;s going to stand up for them?&quot;<br />\n上幾代冇反抗冇爭取搞到香港今時今日咁嘅田地 正正就提醒我哋 如果我哋唔想香港嘅下一代生活喺比依家更差更中國更冇自由嘅香港 依家就要抗爭直至成功為止 <br />\n<br />\n抗爭仲未成功 keep住團火<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"aa59d266cd9e13898ef54030067e22635d8cd106","tid":1298229,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07